org.chocosolver.samples.nsp

Class NurseSchedulingProblem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.chocosolver.samples.nsp.NurseSchedulingProblem
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NSCPModelConstrained

    public class NurseSchedulingProblem
extends Object
    Basis of a Choco CPModel for the Nurse Scheduling Problem. This class defined the model variables and the common utility methods (print, parse, etc.) Constraints should be defined in a derived class
    Author:
    Sophie Demassey
